name: Amir Fachar
note:
Израиль. Technology company. Doing business development and monitization for publishers worldwide. Located in Tel Aviv but also has offices in Dubai. They are looking for publishers in order to offer them their tools and monetization services. Working with 2000 publishers over the world. Нужны очень сильные лидгены (которые назначают много звонков), которые будут находить a lot of publishers in a day.They have a list of websites to get in contact with, send them emails etc. Готов собеседовать через полчаса

Fresh results : Our company is currently working with the client.(10.02.2021)

client_candidates.comment:
1) Lead Generation: Identify potential partners (e.g., publishers, game studios, websites) for monetization opportunities.
2) Outreach: Utilize various methods such as LinkedIn, email, and website contact forms to connect with relevant individuals.
3) Database Management: Create and maintain a database of contacts, including emails, LinkedIn profiles, and other communication details.
4) Follow-ups: Regular communication with leads, including follow-ups and relationship-building with potential partners.
5) Template Utilization: Use provided outreach templates to communicate effectively with leads.
6)Traffic Monetization: Present Adipolo’s value proposition to partners for monetizing their traffic sources.
